<para style="q1">

<verse number="17" style="v" />Yahweh is righteous in all his ways</para>

<para style="q1">and gracious in all he does.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="18" style="v" />Yahweh is near to all those who call to him,</para>

<para style="q1">to all who call to him in trustworthiness.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="19" style="v" />He fulfills the desire of those who honor him;</para>

<para style="q1">he hears their cry and saves them.</para>
